The Marriage Maruade market in Singapore has expanded to keep up with demand from locals seeking a spouse. The market is also catering to foreigners lured to the country after getting wind of Singapore's reputation for religious tolerance and low crime rates. One matchmaker in Singapore says competition has increased with the number of marriage agents mushrooming to meet the rising demand.
